        <div class="text-center mb-12">
           <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Quick Tax Estimator</h2>
           <p class="text-slate-500">연봉을 입력하면 예상 소득세를 3초 만에 계산해 드립니다.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-inner border border-slate-200">
           <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-end">
              <div class="md:col-span-2">
                 <label class="block text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 mb-2">Annual Income (₩)</label>
                 <input type="number" placeholder="Example: 50,000,000" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-300 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-100 transition text-lg bg-white">
              </div>
              <button class="w-full bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/20 text-lg">
                 Calculate
              </button>
           </div>
           
           <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 hidden" id="calc-result">
              <!-- Result will be shown here (JS needed for real function, just placeholder) -->
              <p class="text-center text-slate-500">Calculation is not active in this template.</p>
           </div>
        </div>
     </div>
